verbose_text: Furthermore, the majority of c-kit + cells in the P1 population from the Zfat ZsG/+ fetal liver expressed ZsGreen, and there were also substantial numbers of ZsGreen + cells among the c-kit + P2 cells (XREF_FIG), indicating that Zfat is expressed in c-kit + definitive erythroid progenitor cells, particularly at the P1 and P2 stages.
